      <h1>How to Build Brand Awareness with Strategic Video</h1>
      <p class="lead">See how strategic video content builds brand awareness, drives 1,200% more shares than text, and helps brands connect with their audience.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>January 3, 2025</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 18, 2025</span></p>
    </div>
