<!-- ============ ARTICLE ============ -->
<section class="sec" style="padding-top:40px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="post-wrap post-body reveal">
<p>Brands build awareness with strategic video content by producing memorable, shareable videos that humanize the brand and communicate its values consistently across channels. Video generates 1,200% more shares than text and images combined, making it one of the most effective formats for expanding reach and building lasting recognition.</p><h2>The Power of Brand Awareness Videos</h2><p>Videos don't just capture attention — they humanize a brand, communicate its values, and inspire trust. That combination is why video consistently outperforms static content for visibility and recall.</p><h2>Brand Awareness Is the Foundation of Customer Acquisition</h2><p>Without visibility, even the best products and services can go unnoticed. Building brand awareness means making sure a brand is recognized and remembered before a prospect ever starts actively comparing options — which is exactly what strategic video content is built to do.</p><h2>Viven's Approach to Brand Awareness</h2><p>At Viven, we work with brands to create high-quality video content tailored to their unique identity and goals. These videos are designed to be memorable, shareable, and impactful — increasing reach and visibility while resonating with the audience in a way that sticks.</p><h3>Solutions Offered by Viven</h3><ul><li><a href={p("services/brand-video")}>Brand story videos</a></li><li><a href={p("services/product-video")}>Product videos</a></li><li><a href={p("services/employer-branding")}>Employer branding videos</a></li><li><a href={p("services/social-media-video")}>Social media video campaigns</a></li><li>Event coverage videos</li><li><a href={p("services/how-to-video")}>How-to videos</a></li><li>Behind-the-scenes content</li><li><a href={p("services/corporate-video")}>Corporate overview videos</a></li><li>Animated videos showcasing brand missions</li></ul><h2>Case Study: SV Group's Brand Awareness Campaign</h2><p>SV Group, a major player in the hospitality and gastronomy industry, worked with Viven to produce a video showcasing the dynamic work environment within the company, highlighting the innovative blend of IT and operations behind exceptional experiences. Distributed across multiple platforms, the video enhanced SV Group's brand visibility, attracted high-quality talent, and boosted its reputation as an employer of choice — proof that video content builds recognition and trust while communicating a company's core message. See more examples in our <a href={p("projects")}>portfolio</a>.</p><h2>What Makes a Video Shareable</h2><p>The videos that generate outsized shares tend to share three traits: a clear emotional hook in the first few seconds, a message that's easy to summarize, and a visual style consistent enough that viewers recognize the brand even on mute. Strategic video content is built around these traits rather than around production value alone.</p><h2>Why Brands Trust Viven</h2><ul><li>Expertise in storytelling and visual branding</li><li>High-quality production that aligns with brand image</li><li>Proven success in increasing visibility and audience engagement, as covered in <a href={p("blog/how-brands-build-trust-and-credibility-through-video")}>how brands build trust and credibility through video</a> and <a href={p("blog/boost-brand-growth-with-an-effective-video-marketing-strategy")}>boosting brand growth with an effective video marketing strategy</a></li></ul><p><a href={p("contact")}>Increase your brand awareness with Viven</a>.</p>
    </div>
    <p class="post-service-note"><a href={p("services/brand-video")}>Want to see how this works in practice? Explore our brand video production.</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

